---
/*
  WORK — quieted intro. No mono eyebrow, no big "RECENT WORK. REAL,
  SHIPPED, PAID." header. One short line of context, then the work
  speaks for itself.
*/
---

<section id="work" class="relative py-32 sm:py-44 bg-void">
  <div class="max-w-[1600px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-10 lg:px-14">
    {/* Minimal intro */}
    <div class="mb-16 sm:mb-20 max-w-3xl reveal">
      <h2 class="font-display uppercase leading-[0.9] text-[clamp(40px,6.5vw,88px)] tracking-[-0.01em]">
        Two things I&rsquo;ve <span class="text-gold">shipped</span>.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-paper leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
        Both still running. Both built solo, from sketch to live.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-4 sm:gap-6 auto-rows-[minmax(280px,auto)]">
      {/* ===== BaitIQ — featured ===== */}
      <article
        class="reveal lg:col-span-12 group relative overflow-hidden border border-iron hover:border-gold/60 transition-all duration-500 bg-coal"
      >
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-coal via-honey/20 to-graphite"></div>
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.5]"
          style="background-image: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(168,133,74,0.15) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(168,133,74,0.15) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 40px 40px;"
        ></div>

        <div class="relative flex flex-col gap-8 sm:gap-10 p-6 sm:p-10">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
            <span class="font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.22em] text-bone/70 uppercase">
              I &mdash; 2026
            </span>
            <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-bone/70 text-right">
              iOS · React Native · OpenAI
            </span>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 sm:gap-12 items-center">
            <div class="md:col-span-5 flex flex-col gap-5 order-2 md:order-1">
              <div class="relative w-fit">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 -m-3 bg-gold/15 blur-2xl rounded-full"></div>
                <img
                  src="/projects/baitiq-icon.png"
                  alt="BaitIQ app icon"
                  width="120"
                  height="120"
                  loading="lazy"
                  class="relative w-16 sm:w-20 h-auto rounded-[24%] shadow-[0_15px_30px_-10px_rgba(0,0,0,0.4)] ring-1 ring-iron"
                />
              </div>

              <h3
                class="font-display uppercase text-[clamp(48px,6.5vw,96px)] leading-[0.95] tracking-[-0.02em] transition-colors duration-500 group-hover:text-gold"
              >
                BaitIQ
              </h3>

              <p class="text-paper text-lg leading-snug max-w-md">
                AI fishing intelligence. Point your camera, get bait
                recommendations tuned for your weather, location, and
                conditions.
                <span class="text-bone">Live on the iOS App Store.</span>
              </p>

              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mt-2">
                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 bg-void/80 border border-iron rounded-full text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-mono text-bone/90">
                  <span class="relative flex w-1.5 h-1.5">
                    <span class="absolute inline-flex w-full h-full rounded-full bg-[#22c55e] opacity-75 animate-ping"></span>
                    <span class="relative inline-flex w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#22c55e]"></span>
                  </span>
                  Live on the App Store
                </span>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 bg-void/80 border border-iron rounded-full text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-mono text-bone/90">
                  <span class="text-gold tracking-normal text-[13px] leading-none">★★★★★</span>
                  <span>App Store</span>
                </span>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 bg-void/80 border border-iron rounded-full text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-mono text-smoke">
                  v2 shipping this week
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="md:col-span-7 order-1 md:order-2">
              <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 -m-6 bg-gold/10 blur-3xl rounded-full transition-all duration-700 group-hover:bg-gold/20"></div>
                <img
                  src="/projects/baitiq-marketing.png"
                  alt="BaitIQ marketing site shown on a MacBook"
                  width="900"
                  height="900"
                  loading="lazy"
                  class="relative w-full h-auto max-w-[520px] mx-auto transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-[1.04] group-hover:-rotate-[0.5deg]"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      {/* ===== Unlearn ===== */}
      <article
        class="reveal reveal-delay-1 lg:col-span-12 group relative overflow-hidden border border-iron hover:border-gold/60 transition-all duration-500 bg-coal"
      >
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-coal via-honey/20 to-graphite"></div>
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 opacity-50"
          style="background-image: radial-gradient(rgba(45,31,10,0.12) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 8px 8px;"
        ></div>

        <div class="relative flex flex-col gap-8 sm:gap-10 p-6 sm:p-10">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
            <span class="font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.22em] text-bone/70 uppercase">
              II &mdash; 2026
            </span>
            <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-bone/70 text-right">
              Brand · Site · Strategy
            </span>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 sm:gap-12 items-center">
            <div class="md:col-span-5 flex flex-col gap-5 order-2 md:order-1">
              <h3
                class="font-display uppercase text-[clamp(40px,5.5vw,72px)] leading-[0.95] tracking-[-0.02em] transition-colors duration-500 group-hover:text-gold"
              >
                Unlearn Your Credit Habits
              </h3>

              <p class="text-paper text-lg leading-snug max-w-md">
                Brand identity and conversion-focused landing site for a
                credit education business. Custom-designed in Astro, with
                payment and booking integrations.
                <span class="text-bone">From sketch to staged in twelve weeks.</span>
              </p>

              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mt-2">
                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 bg-void/80 border border-iron rounded-full text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-mono text-bone/90">
                  Launching Q3 2026
                </span>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 bg-void/80 border border-iron rounded-full text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-mono text-bone/90">
                  12 weeks · solo
                </span>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 bg-void/80 border border-iron rounded-full text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-mono text-smoke">
                  Astro · Tailwind · Stripe
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="md:col-span-7 order-1 md:order-2">
              <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 -m-6 bg-gold/10 blur-3xl rounded-full transition-all duration-700 group-hover:bg-gold/20"></div>
                <img
                  src="/projects/unlearn-marketing.png"
                  alt="Unlearn Your Credit Habits marketing site shown on a MacBook"
                  width="900"
                  height="900"
                  loading="lazy"
                  class="relative w-full h-auto max-w-[520px] mx-auto transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-[1.04] group-hover:rotate-[0.5deg]"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
